be rotted by drugs!

481
00:24:07.166 --> 00:24:09.291
[in Arabic] May God forgive
us! What is this filth?!

482
00:24:10.166 --> 00:24:13.500
[sighs] Okay. enough. Get out.

483
00:24:13.583 --> 00:24:16.166
I need to take her to the
school. She's going to be late.

484
00:24:26.291 --> 00:24:30.875
[sighs] Habibti. I am sorry
she did that to you. Teta...

485
00:24:30.958 --> 00:24:32.809
[in Arabic] I don't know what's
happening to her these days.

486
00:24:32.833 --> 00:24:34.916
Maybe dementia or Alzheimer.

487
00:24:35.166 --> 00:24:37.541
She never knew how to
relate to her daughter.

488
00:24:37.625 --> 00:24:41.708
So different than you and
me and how close we are

489
00:24:41.791 --> 00:24:44.750
and how we know every little
thing about each other.

490
00:24:44.833 --> 00:24:46.708
Classic mother-daughter
relation...

491
00:24:46.791 --> 00:24:47.791
I'm gay.

492
00:24:48.291 --> 00:24:49.458
Um...

493
00:24:49.583 --> 00:24:51.666
[coughing]

494
00:24:52.666 --> 00:24:55.458
This is your fault! I
knew it. Astaghfurillah.

495
00:24:55.583 --> 00:24:58.375
[coughing]

496
00:25:00.041 --> 00:25:02.666
[dramatic music]

